The best way I can describe stem cell treatment is life-changing. Forget everything you know about medicine, everything you’ve been told in the United States about how great our medicine is. Now start with the simple premise, American medicine is milking us like cows.  Our system is broken and quite honestly it sucks. There’s no money in the cure. The money is in the treatment.
